rs":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아뇨, 실은……\n저번에 토모에 짱이 감기 때문에 고생했거든요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"토모에 짱한테 뭔가 해줄 수 있는 게 없을까 생각했는데\n병문안은 감기 옮으면 큰일이라고\n본인한테 거절당했거든요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그때 사아야 짱이 토모에 짱한테 간식거리를 주러 간다고\n하는 이야기를 들었어요. 그래서 참지 못하고\n저도 간식거리를 주러 가기로 했어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"제가 준 간식 말인가요?\n생강 홍차에요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"생강 홍차를 마시면\n몸이 속에서부터 따뜻해져서\n감기에 걸렸을 때 딱 좋겠다 싶어서요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그런…… 별로 대단한 일을 한 것도 아니에요!\n친구가 몸이 안 좋다면\n걱정되는 게 당연하잖아요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그리고 역시 토모에 짱이 학교에 없으면\n허전하기도 하고 밴드 멤버도 다섯 명이 다 모이지 않으면\n안심이 되지 않기도 하고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아, 참고로 토모에 짱은\n이제 다 나았어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아코 짱의 간호 덕분에\n아주 건강해져서\n지금은 학교에도 잘 나오고 있어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그래도 이제 막 나은 참이니까.\n밴드 연습은 함께하지 못하고 있어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"좀 더 상태를 살피고\n완전히 괜찮다! 라는 확신이 들면\n다 같이 연습을 다시 시작할 참이에요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"후우~ 빨리 그날이 와야 할 텐데~\n다시 다섯 명이서 연주하는 게\n벌써 기대돼서 어쩔 줄 모르겠어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId